---

## 📌 Project Overview

This project implements an **end-to-end Healthcare Analytics Data Pipeline** using the **Medallion Architecture (Bronze → Silver → Gold)** in **Databricks** with **PySpark**, **Delta Lake**, and **Spark SQL**.

The pipeline ingests raw healthcare CSV files, performs data cleansing and transformation, creates business-ready analytics tables, and visualizes key healthcare metrics using Databricks Dashboards.

---

## 🚀 Architecture

```
                CSV Files
                    │
                    ▼
        🥉 Bronze Layer (Raw Data)
                    │
                    ▼
      🥈 Silver Layer (Clean & Validated)
                    │
                    ▼
      🥇 Gold Layer (Business Analytics)
                    │
                    ▼
      📊 Databricks Dashboard
```

---

## 📂 Dataset

The project uses five healthcare datasets:

- 👤 Patients
- 👨‍⚕️ Doctors
- 📅 Appointments
- 💳 Billing
- 💉 Treatments

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Databricks Community Edition
- PySpark
- Spark SQL
- Delta Lake
- Unity Catalog
- Git & GitHub

