---

# 🥉 Bronze Layer

The Bronze layer stores the raw healthcare data exactly as received.

### Features

- CSV ingestion
- Metadata-driven loading
- Audit logging
- Delta tables
- Raw data preservation

Tables:

- bronze.patients
- bronze.doctors
- bronze.appointments
- bronze.billing
- bronze.treatments

---

# 🥈 Silver Layer

The Silver layer performs data cleansing and validation.

### Data Processing

- Removed duplicate records
- Standardized date formats
- Converted data types
- Null value handling
- Data quality validation
- Business rule enforcement

Tables:

- silver.patients
- silver.doctors
- silver.appointments
- silver.billing
- silver.treatments

---

# 🥇 Gold Layer

The Gold layer contains business-ready analytical tables.

### Gold Tables

### 1. KPI Dashboard

Provides executive-level KPIs such as:

- Total Patients
- Total Doctors
- Total Appointments
- Total Revenue
- Average Bill
- Appointment Completion Rate

---

### 2. Doctor Performance

Includes:

- Total Appointments
- Revenue Generated
- Average Bill
- Doctor-wise Performance

---

### 3. Patient Analytics

Includes:

- Patient Age Groups
- Gender Distribution
- Insurance Provider Analysis
- Total Billing

---

### 4. Revenue Summary

Includes:

- Monthly Revenue
- Payment Methods
- Payment Status
- Average Revenue

---

# 📊 Dashboard

The Databricks Dashboard contains:

✅ KPI Cards

- Total Patients
- Total Doctors
- Total Appointments
- Total Revenue
- Average Bill

✅ Charts

- 📈 Monthly Revenue Trend
- 🥧 Appointment Status Distribution
- 👨‍⚕️ Doctor Performance
- 🛡 Insurance Provider Analysis
- 👥 Patient Age Distribution

