---

## ▶️ How to Run

1. Import all notebooks into Databricks.
2. Upload the CSV datasets.
3. Run notebooks in order:

```
01_setup_metadata

↓

02_bronze_ingestion

↓

03–07 Silver Layer

↓

08–11 Gold Layer
```

4. Open the Databricks Dashboard.

